                        <h3>General Representative 2</h3>
                        <div class="rating"><span class="number">4</span>Platform quality</div>
                        <div class="rating"><span class="number">2</span>Platform completion</div>
                        <div class="rating"><span class="number">4</span>Fulfillment of responsibilities</div>
